# CODEOWNERS — lq-maintainer-agent
#
# Security-routes the judgment-bearing and permission-bearing surfaces
# (design doc §3.6). Together with branch protection, these paths require
# review from the security team; CONTRIBUTING.md additionally requires
# two maintainer reviews for rules/, hooks/, settings/, and skills/
# frontmatter.
#
# NOTE: while the repo lives under the personal account @houfu, that
# account owns all routes. On transfer to the legalquants org, replace
# with the security team (e.g. @legalquants/maintainer-agent-security).

/rules/           @houfu
# The reading-deck glossary is normative (a wrong plain-language gloss
# misrepresents a security decision — design §8.6); route it like rules/.
/templates/deck/  @houfu
/hooks/           @houfu
/settings/        @houfu
/skills/          @houfu
/.claude-plugin/  @houfu

# CODEOWNERS itself is a permission surface too.
/CODEOWNERS       @houfu
